Edgars Stores of Zimbabwe Receives $5 Million Loan to Pay Debt

-- B y   B r i a n   L a t h a m
-- 
2011-07-04T11:41:40Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-07-04/edgars-stores-of-zimbabwe-receives-5-million-loan-to-pay-debt.html
Edgars Stores Zimbabwe Ltd. (EDGARS) , a
clothing retailer, secured a $5 million loan from an
unidentified Zimbabwean bank, African Corporate Announcements
said in an e-mailed  statement  today.  The loan will be used to pay debt, Harare-based African
Corporate Announcements said. Edgars is 40 percent-owned by
Edgars Consolidated Stores Ltd., the South African unit of Bain
Capital LLC.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Brian Latham in Johannesburg at 
 blatham@bloomberg.net   To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  